I see... There are two
broken parts, sir.

repairs will be complete, sir.

rows.label: qst201712_msg2001
rows.name: What kind of parts do you need?

A Search Monitor and
a Delta Vessel, sir.

rows.label: qst201712_msg2003
rows.name:
I believe these parts can be
obtained through salvaging, sir.

rows.label: qst201712_msg0004
rows.name:
Then it's my turn! Let's go
get those parts right away!
